Title: Bucks win 139-112 in Timberwolves coach Chris Finch's debut
Description: Giannis Antetokounmpo and the Milwaukee Bucks demonstrated the magnitude of the challenge facing new Minnesota Timberwolves coach Chris Finch. Antetokoumpo had 37 points, eight rebounds and eight assists as the Bucks won 139-112 on Tuesday to spoil Finch’s debut.
Author: The Canadian Press on MSN.com
